Package: planktonr
Title: Analysis and visualisation of plankton data
Version: 0.3.5.0000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jason D.", "Everett", , "jase.everett@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6681-8054")),
    person("Claire H.", "Davies", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0424-1835"))
  )
Description: planktonr is an r package that facilitates the download, analysis and visualisation of phytoplankton and zooplankton data. Our initial focus will be on plankton data stored on the Australian Ocean Data Network ([AODN](https://portal.aodn.org.au)) and collected by the Integrated Marine Observing System ([IMOS](www.imos.org.au)), but we hope to expand to other plankton data sets in the future.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/PlanktonTeam/planktonr
BugReports: https://github.com/PlanktonTeam/planktonr/issues
